fields.description:
Partners provide leads very early in the student's journey. 

Most partners are education consultants, that help student get an admission in universities. Therefore they engage with students maybe months ahead of student actually looking for accommodation. However these partners share leads with amber once they have received some interest from student. 

However if these leads are now uploaded, these get assigned and agent makes calls to students, while most would land up in opportunity or worst case in lost as “not interested”.

However later some of these leads might come in organically, but then many of the parent leads being in lost, the attribution to partner is lost, as the lead which goes to won could be from say organic or google adwords

It is preferred that these leads are logged in system, but are contacted only on user action (say lead places enquiry with us or if say partner has informed us to make the enquiry)

Most partners are education consultants, that help student get an admission in universities. Therefore they engage with students maybe months ahead of student actually looking for accommodation. However these partners share leads with amber once they have received some interest from student. 

However if these leads are now uploaded, these get assigned and agent makes calls to students, while most would land up in opportunity or worst case in lost as “not interested”.

However later some of these leads might come in organically, but then many of the parent leads being in lost, the attribution to partner is lost, as the lead which goes to won could be from say organic or google adwords
